    "body": "Instead of running `geth console` within a `screen` session, I recommend that you run `geth` by itself within a screen session, and use `geth attach` to get a console. \r\n\r\nI'm guessing that the console-handler picks up on the `ctrl-A-D` and exits, since I never have this problem myself when running geth (without `console`) within `screen`. ",
